Interface EAPActivity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Module
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EAPDisplay

    public interface EAPActivity
extends Module
    The interface which all EAPActivities must extend. This is defined to allow mockable activities.

    v0.0.1-alpha
    Author:
